CHOLERA - BOLIVIA (02)
**********************
A ProMED-mail post
See Also
Cholera - Bolivia 980222225139
Date: Mon, 23 Feb 1998 07:47:51 +0000
From: Steve Berger <mberger@post.tau.ac.il>

The following background data on cholera in Bolivia were extracted from the
GIDEON software program:
In recent years, most cases have been reported from Beni, Chuquisaca,
Cochabamba, El Alto, La Paz, Oruro, Potosi, Riberalta, Santa Cruz, Tarija
and Tupiza Departments.
Year Cases Fatal
1991 206 12
1992 23,645 383
1993 10,134 254
1994 1,710 46
1995 2,293 54
1996 2,847 68
1997 * 1,147 12
* preliminary data
During 1997, activity was centered in Tarija (492 cases), with additional
cases in Beni, Potosi and Santa Cruz.
--
Dr. Steve Berger
e-mail: mberger@post.tau.ac.il
